# Run-Epics Slack (Mandatory)

When executing `/run-epics`, you MUST run these scripts at the specified steps. Do not skip.

| Step | Script | When |
|------|--------|------|
| a2 | `scripts/ci/slack_post_epic_checklist.sh` | First action when epic starts (before step b) |
| f | `scripts/ci/slack_post_review.sh` with verdict args | After each review pass (before merge) |
| i | `scripts/ci/gh_pr_merge_with_notify.sh` | For merge — never use raw `gh pr merge` |

Scripts no-op if webhooks are unset; they must still be run.
